{"tid":2369913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賀錦麗據報將辭去代表加州的國會參議員職務","createTime":"2021-01-17T14:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T14:42:23.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02be94f5c1d8cab782a0cc6e0429489fda28910f","tid":2369913,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"美國候任副總統賀錦麗據報將在當地星期一，辭去代表加州的國會參議員職務。報道說，賀錦麗將不會向參議院發表告別演說，參議院將在總統就職禮前一日，即是當地星期二舉行會議。加州州長紐瑟姆已經提名州務卿帕迪拉接替賀錦麗，完成她餘下兩年的參議員任期。<br />\n<br />\n2021-01-17 22:10:20<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570894-20210117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570894-20210117.htm&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=91d925ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570894-20210117.htm&h=9e593845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570894-20210117.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9378c079d2afb53283cb6d6194c73b25ecddad78","tid":2369913,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />準備坐正"},{"pid":"ba821f5dbff9d4a25419124eab882bdc08b2acd9","tid":2369913,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"我侵穩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49e9a23788927d9edee92a94288e82b29b0d427","tid":2369913,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba821f5dbff9d4a25419124eab882bdc08b2acd9","tid":2369913,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"我侵穩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"*登先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65867a9f1cfc8